						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "Europe/Berlin"
					},
					"body": "I tried it in a module which works. Please see this line.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/WappZapp/html5video-appcelerator-module/blob/master/src/tv/wappzapp/html5video/WebVideoProxy.java#L94\r\n\r\nShouldn't be that hard of a fix. I like the way you guys do it way better.",
